explanation.details: Hnh nh sng in tim cho thy nhp tim u v n nh. Nhp tim hin ti l 74 ln/pht, nm trong khong bnh thng (60-100 ln/pht). Thi gian dn truyn in tim (QRS duration) l 0.081 giy (tng ng 81 ms), theo hng dn y khoa, y l mt QRS hp v nm trong gii hn bnh thng (70-100 ms), cho thy tn hiu in truyn i qua cc bung tim di mt cch hiu qu v khng b cn tr. Cc ch s khc nh bin  sng R (R Wave Amplitude) 6.197 mV v nng lng tn hiu (Signal Energy) 1621.6132 u phn nh hot ng in tim khe mnh. Tt c cc ch s u cho thy hot ng in tim n nh v khng c du hiu bt thng.
